# Baked into the dashboard at build time (`vite build` = production mode).
# Committed on purpose so the deployed dashboard always knows the API URL,
# independent of any Cloudflare build-variable setting. The API URL is public,
# not a secret. Dev (`vite`) ignores this file and uses the localhost proxy.
VITE_API_BASE=https://annrashtra-dst-api.onrender.com
